le style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Chelsea 2018 hot nh\u1ea5t ng\u00e0y 0308 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Chelsea 2018 hot nh\u1ea5t ng\u00e0y 0308 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/5/20/Chuyen-nhuong-Chelsea-2018-hot-nhat-ngay-0308-hinh-anh.PNG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Chelsea kh\u00f4ng b\u00e1n Courtois cho Real</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nT\u01b0\u01a1ng lai Thibaut Courtois \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Chelsea quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh, theo Daily Express \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh London kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh kh\u00f4ng b\u00e1n c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 26 tu\u1ed5i cho Real Madrid \u1edf H\u00e8 2018.<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/chelsea-dua-ra-quyet-dinh-cuoi-cung-ve-tuong-lai-courtois-172-192624.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/3/15/chelsea-dua-ra-quyet-dinh-cuoi-cung-ve-tuong-lai-courtois.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/chelsea-dua-ra-quyet-dinh-cuoi-cung-ve-tuong-lai-courtois-172-192624.html\">Chelsea \u0111\u01b0a ra quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai Courtois</span><br>\r\nT\u01b0\u01a1ng lai Thibaut Courtois \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Chelsea quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh, theo Daily Express \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh London kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh kh\u00f4ng b\u00e1n c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 26 tu\u1ed5i cho Real Madrid \u1edf H\u00e8 2018.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Zaha b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd mu\u1ed1n t\u1edbi Chelsea</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Wilfried Zaha mu\u1ed1n t\u1edbi Chelsea, ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1edd Bi\u1ec3n Ng\u00e0 \u0111\u00e3 t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i gia h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi Crystal Palace \u0111\u1ec3 quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m t\u1edbi Stamford Bridge.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>M\u1ee5c ti\u00eau c\u1ee7a Chelsea \u0111\u1ed3ng \u00fd \u1edf l\u1ea1i Serie A</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong m\u1ed9t di\u1ec5n bi\u1ebfn m\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 ch\u1ea1y c\u00e1nh Alessandro Florenzi \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ed3ng \u00fd gia h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi AS Roma k\u1ebft th\u00fac nh\u1eefng tin \u0111\u1ed3n chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng li\u00ean quan t\u1edbi CLB Chelsea.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Atletico Madrid b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd mu\u1ed1n g\u00e2y s\u1ed1c v\u1edbi Batshuayi</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Batshuayi choi an tuong voi mot cu dup\" title=\"Batshuayi ch\u01a1i \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u1edbi m\u1ed9t c\u00fa \u0111\u00fap\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/1/28/Tien-dao-Batshuayi-noi-gi-sau-cu-dup-vao-luoi-Newcastle-hinh-anh-2.JPG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Atletico mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 Batshuayi&nbsp;</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Atletico Madrid mu\u1ed1n mua Michy Batshuayi t\u1eeb Chelsea, theo L'Equipe, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a T\u00e2y Ban Nha ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi 30 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng mua c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ec9.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Pickford l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng tr\u01b0\u1edbc tin \u0111\u1ed3n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Chelsea quan t\u00e2m</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Jordan Pickford n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh mu\u1ed1n g\u1eafn b\u00f3 v\u1edbi Everton h\u01a1n l\u00e0 chuy\u1ec3n t\u1edbi kho\u00e1c \u00e1o Chelsea \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Nh\u1edd John Terry, Chelsea s\u1eafp c\u00f3 t\u00e2n binh 20 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chelsea mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 Jack Grealish c\u1ee7a Aston Villa, nh\u1edd huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i John Terry \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh London s\u1eafp s\u1edf h\u1eefu c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 22 tu\u1ed5i.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Olivier Giroud c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 r\u1eddi Chelsea v\u00e0o ng\u00e0y cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng k\u1ef3 CN H\u00e8 2018</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng Olivier Giroud r\u1eddi Chelsea \u1edf k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng H\u00e8 2018 l\u00e0 v\u1eabn c\u00f2n, ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 b\u1ecb \u0111\u1ea9y \u0111i \u1edf nh\u1eefng ng\u00e0y cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng \u1edf H\u00e8 n\u00e0y.<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/olivier-giroud-co-the-roi-chelsea-vao-ngay-cuoi-cung-ky-cn-he-2018-172-192518.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/5/9/olivier-giroud-co-the-roi-chelsea-vao-ngay-cuoi-cung-ky-cn-he-2018.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/olivier-giroud-co-the-roi-chelsea-vao-ngay-cuoi-cung-ky-cn-he-2018-172-192518.html\">Olivier Giroud c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 r\u1eddi Chelsea v\u00e0o ng\u00e0y cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng k\u1ef3 CN H\u00e8 2018</span><br>\r\nKh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng Olivier Giroud r\u1eddi Chelsea \u1edf k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng H\u00e8 2018 l\u00e0 v\u1eabn c\u00f2n, ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 b\u1ecb \u0111\u1ea9y \u0111i \u1edf nh\u1eefng ng\u00e0y cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng \u1edf H\u00e8 n\u00e0y.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Chelsea c\u00f3 ph\u01b0\u01a1ng \u00e1n B ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u1ee5 Aaron Ramsey</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chelsea mu\u1ed1n mua Mateo Kovacic c\u1ee7a Real Madrid trong tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Aaron Ramsey c\u1ee7a Arsenal, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 th\u00f4ng tin \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u1edd Daily Mail c\u1ee7a n\u01b0\u1edbc Anh \u0111\u0103ng t\u1ea3i.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Barkley quy\u1ebft chi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u00ec v\u1ecb tr\u00ed t\u1ea1i Chelsea</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Ross Barkley co co hoi da chinh khi Chelsea khong chieu mo thanh cong Golovin\" title=\"Ross Barkley c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh khi Chelsea kh\u00f4ng chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng Golovin\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/31/bas.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Ross Barkley kh\u00f4ng r\u1eddi Chelsea</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ross Barkley quy\u1ebft t\u00ecm l\u1ea1i v\u1ecb tr\u00ed \u1edf Chelsea. Ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 24 tu\u1ed5i \u0111\u00e3 tr\u1ea3i qua c\u01a1n \u00e1c m\u1ed9ng n\u1eeda cu\u1ed1i m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i tr\u01b0\u1edbc d\u00f9 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1eb7t nhi\u1ec1u hy v\u1ecdng.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Chelsea d\u00f9ng bom ti\u1ec1n gi\u1eef ch\u00e2n nh\u00e0 v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch World Cup 2018</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chelsea gia h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi Kante, h\u1ecd ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn \u0111\u00e1p \u1ee9ng cho c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p m\u1ee9c l\u01b0\u01a1ng 290.000 b\u1ea3ng/tu\u1ea7n, qua \u0111\u00f3 gi\u1eef anh \u1edf l\u1ea1i Stamford Bridge.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Stoke Ctiy ng\u0103n c\u1ea3n Butland t\u1edbi Chelsea</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Chelsea 2018 mua Jack Butland c\u1ee7a Stoke City th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng \u0111ang l\u00e0 kh\u00e1 th\u1ea5p. HLV Gary Rowett c\u1ee7a Stoke tuy\u00ean b\u1ed1 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 25 tu\u1ed5i s\u1ebd \u1edf l\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Bet365.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNguy\u1ec5n Huy\u1ec1n (TTVN)</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1937","checkdouble":"192630"},{"date":"07:06 03/08","title":"Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam s\u1ebd \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u Palestine b\u1eb1ng \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh n\u00e0o?","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/1/olympic-viet-nam-se-doi-dau-palestine-bang-doi-hinh-nao.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>\u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam s\u1ebd c\u00f3 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u khai m\u00e0n chi\u1ebfn d\u1ecbch ASIAD 2018 v\u1edbi cu\u1ed9c \u0111\u1ecd s\u1ee9c v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 Palestine v\u00e0o t\u1ed1i nay 3/8. V\u00e0 li\u1ec7u HLV Park Hang Seo s\u1ebd s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh n\u00e0o \u1edf tr\u1eadn n\u00e0y?</h2><h2>1. Th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n \u0110\u1eb7ng V\u0103n L\u00e2m<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u1ea1i ASIAD s\u1eafp t\u1edbi, HLV Park Hang Seo s\u1ebd ch\u1ec9 mang theo hai th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n. V\u00e0 \u0110\u1eb7ng V\u0103n L\u00e2m ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 g\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u1eb7t nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 tin t\u01b0\u1edfng l\u1edbn nh\u1ea5t t\u1eeb th\u1ea7y Park l\u00fac n\u00e0y.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ch\u00ednh th\u1ea7y Park c\u0169ng th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn chuy\u1ec7n n\u00e0y: &ldquo;Theo t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1, V\u0103n L\u00e2m v\u1eabn \u0111ang l\u00e0 l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t b\u1edfi Ti\u1ebfn D\u0169ng v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a c\u00f3 v\u1ecb tr\u00ed v\u1eefng ch\u1eafc \u1edf FLC Thanh Ho\u00e1.&nbsp;T\u1ea5t nhi\u00ean, v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 c\u1ee7a Ti\u1ebfn D\u0169ng c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng qu\u00e1 nghi\u00eam tr\u1ecdng, \u0111\u01a1n gi\u1ea3n ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 v\u00ec c\u1eadu \u1ea5y kh\u00f4ng th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c thi \u0111\u1ea5u trong th\u1eddi gian g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y&rdquo;.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"\u0110\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam s\u1ebd \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u Palestine nh\u01b0 th\u1ebf n\u00e0o h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"\u0110\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam s\u1ebd \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u Palestine nh\u01b0 th\u1ebf n\u00e0o h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/1/Doi-hinh-Olympic-Viet-Nam-se-doi-dau-Palestine-nhu-the-nao-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>&nbsp;</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Do \u0111\u00f3, kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng V\u0103n L\u00e2m ra s\u00e2n \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1edbi l\u00e0 r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn. \u0110\u00e2y c\u0169ng l\u00e0 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ec3 ng\u00f4i sao \u0111ang kho\u00e1c \u00e1o CLB H\u1ea3i Ph\u00f2ng th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n, qua \u0111\u00f3 kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh v\u1ecb tr\u00ed ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c tr\u00ean tuy\u1ec3n.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<h2>2. H\u1eadu v\u1ec7 c\u00e1nh ph\u1ea3i V\u0103n Thanh<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c c\u1ea3 hai h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 H\u1ed3ng Duy l\u1eabn Xu\u00e2n M\u1ea1nh \u0111\u1ec1u g\u1eb7p ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng, V\u0103n Thanh ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 g\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u1eb7t s\u00e1ng gi\u00e1 nh\u1ea5t b\u00ean h\u00e0nh lang c\u00e1nh ph\u1ea3i trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 qu\u00ea H\u1ea3i D\u01b0\u01a1ng s\u1edf h\u1eefu k\u1ef9 thu\u1eadt, t\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ed9 v\u00e0 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng s\u00fat xa kh\u00e1 \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng. V\u0103n Thanh ch\u01a1i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c v\u1ecb tr\u00ed h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 bi\u00ean, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 v\u00e0 ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o. \u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 l\u00fd do gi\u00fap anh s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ea7y Park trao c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1edbi.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<h2>3. Trung v\u1ec7 Ti\u1ebfn D\u0169ng<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u00f3 th\u1ec3 n\u00f3i B\u00f9i Ti\u1ebfn D\u0169ng \u0111ang \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 l\u00e0 th\u1ee7 l\u0129nh h\u00e0ng ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 c\u1ee7a Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam l\u00fac n\u00e0y, sau khi Qu\u1ebf Ng\u1ecdc H\u1ea3i kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tri\u1ec7u t\u1eadp. Thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111i\u1ec1m t\u0129nh, t\u1ef1 tin, Ti\u1ebfn D\u0169ng ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn s\u1ebd l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t ch\u1ed7 d\u1ef1a tinh th\u1ea7n cho c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i trong c\u00e1c tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1edbi.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Trung ve Bui Tien Dung ghi ban cho Viettel trong ngay thay Park den du khan\" title=\"Trung v\u1ec7 B\u00f9i Ti\u1ebfn D\u0169ng ghi b\u00e0n cho Viettel trong ng\u00e0y th\u1ea7y Park \u0111\u1ebfn d\u1ef1 kh\u00e1n\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/5/28/HLV-Park-Hang-Seo-du-khan,-trung-ve-Bui-Tien-Dung-toa-sang-ruc-ro-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>&nbsp;</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>4. Trung v\u1ec7 \u0110\u1ed7 Duy M\u1ea1nh<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong b\u1ed1i c\u1ea3nh ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i \u1edf CLB H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i l\u00e0 \u0110\u00ecnh Tr\u1ecdng \u0111ang g\u1eb7p ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng, \u0110\u1ed7 Duy M\u1ea1nh nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng s\u1ebd l\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ra s\u00e2n \u1edf tr\u1eadn Vi\u1ec7t Nam g\u1eb7p Palestine. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u1ede m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u00e0y, Duy M\u1ea1nh c\u0169ng duy tr\u00ec phong \u0111\u1ed9 kh\u00e1 cao t\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00f4. L\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i m\u1ea1nh m\u1ebd, l\u0103n x\u1ea3 c\u1ee7a Duy M\u1ea1nh s\u1ebd gi\u00fap h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u1ea5t th\u00e9p v\u00e0 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ee9ng v\u1eefng tr\u01b0\u1edbc s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<h2>5. H\u1eadu v\u1ec7 c\u00e1nh tr\u00e1i \u0110o\u00e0n V\u0103n H\u1eadu<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Gi\u1ed1ng nh\u01b0 Duy M\u1ea1nh, V\u0103n H\u1eadu \u0111ang c\u00f3 phong \u0111\u1ed9 kh\u00e1 cao trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o CLB H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i. Tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i sau m\u1ed9t th\u1eddi gian d\u00e0i \u0111i\u1ec1u tr\u1ecb ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng, V\u0103n H\u1eadu \u0111\u00e3 qu\u00e1n xuy\u1ebfn kh\u00e1 t\u1ed1t h\u00e0nh lang c\u00e1nh tr\u00e1i c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00f4. Anh th\u1eadm ch\u00ed c\u00f2n ghi b\u00e0n gi\u00fap H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i tho\u00e1t thua \u1edf nh\u1eefng tr\u1eadn c\u1ea7u g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">S\u1edf h\u1eefu chi\u1ec1u cao \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u00f9ng kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng l\u00ean c\u00f4ng, v\u1ec1 th\u1ee7 nh\u1ecbp nh\u00e0ng, V\u0103n H\u1eadu h\u1ee9a h\u1eb9n s\u1ebd l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t c\u00e1i t\u00ean s\u1ebd t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng t\u1ea1i ASIAD s\u1eafp t\u1edbi.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hlv-uzbekistan-an-tuong-voi-hai-cau-thu-cua-olympic-viet-nam-168-192545.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/16/hlv-uzbekistan-an-tuong-voi-hai-cau-thu-cua-olympic-viet-nam.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hlv-uzbekistan-an-tuong-voi-hai-cau-thu-cua-olympic-viet-nam-168-192545.html\">HLV Uzbekistan \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u1edbi hai c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam</span><br>\r\nChia s\u1ebb trong bu\u1ed5i h\u1ecdp b\u00e1o tr\u01b0\u1edbc gi\u1ea3i giao h\u1eefu t\u1ee9 h\u00f9ng c\u00fap Vinaphone 2018, HLV tr\u01b0\u1edfng \u0110T U23 Uzbekistan \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng l\u1eddi nh\u1eadn x\u00e9t v\u1ec1 \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 Vi\u1ec7t Nam.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>6. Ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 c\u00e1nh Phan V\u0103n \u0110\u1ee9c<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110ang c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng t\u1ea1i SLNA, Phan V\u0103n \u0110\u1ee9c g\u1ea7n nh\u01b0 s\u1ebd ch\u1eafc su\u1ea5t thi \u0111\u1ea5u trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam. V\u1edbi th\u1ec3 l\u1ef1c b\u1ec1n b\u1ec9 c\u00f9ng kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng c\u1ef1c t\u1ed1t v\u1edbi 9 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng cho \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng x\u1ee9 Ngh\u1ec7 \u1edf V-League m\u00f9a n\u00e0y, V\u0103n \u0110\u1ee9c r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t ni\u1ec1m hy v\u1ecdng c\u1ee7a th\u1ea7y Park \u1edf gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1edbi.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Phan Van Duc dang co phong do cao voi bon ban sau ba tran gan nhat.\" title=\"Phan V\u0103n \u0110\u1ee9c \u0111ang c\u00f3 phong \u0111\u1ed9 cao v\u1edbi b\u1ed1n b\u00e0n sau ba tr\u1eadn g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t.\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/6/a1-7074-1530882860.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>&nbsp;</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>7. Ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 L\u01b0\u01a1ng Xu\u00e2n Tr\u01b0\u1eddng<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Xu\u00e2n Tr\u01b0\u1eddng ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn s\u1ebd l\u00e0 c\u00e1i t\u00ean kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 thi\u1ebfu c\u1ee7a Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u1edf ASIAD s\u1eafp t\u1edbi. V\u00e0 tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p Palestine s\u1ebd l\u00e0 d\u1ecbp \u0111\u1ec3 ng\u00f4i sao HAGL th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n n\u0103ng l\u1ef1c v\u00e0 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng \u0111i\u1ec1u ti\u1ebft tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u1ede m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u00e0y, Xu\u00e2n Tr\u01b0\u1eddng \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c kh\u00f4ng \u00edt b\u00e0n th\u1eafng c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o b\u00e0n th\u1eafng cho c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i. Do \u0111\u00f3 \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1edbi, th\u1ee7 qu\u00e2n U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam s\u1ebd c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t su\u1ea5t \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<h2>8. Ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 \u0110\u1ed7 H\u00f9ng D\u0169ng<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">L\u00e0 m\u1eabu ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 \u0111a n\u0103ng, H\u00f9ng D\u0169ng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 s\u1ebd l\u00e0 c\u00e1i t\u00ean s\u1ebd \u0111\u00e1 c\u1eb7p c\u00f9ng Xu\u00e2n Tr\u01b0\u1eddng n\u01a1i trung t\u00e2m h\u00e0ng ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7. Thi \u0111\u1ea5u m\u1ea1nh m\u1ebd, l\u0103n x\u1ea3 v\u00e0 c\u00f3 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng tung ra nh\u1eefng \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng chuy\u1ec1n d\u00e0i gi\u00e0u t\u00ednh \u0111\u1ed9t bi\u1ebfn, H\u00f9ng D\u0169ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c xem s\u1ebd l\u00e0 ph\u00e1t hi\u1ec7n m\u1edbi c\u1ee7a HLV Park Hang Seo \u1edf gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u l\u1ea7n n\u00e0y. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u1ed7 H\u00f9ng D\u0169ng c\u0169ng l\u00e0 1 trong s\u1ed1 4 g\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u1eb7t c\u1ee7a H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i \u0111\u00e3 thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u1ee7 20 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ea1i V-League m\u00f9a n\u00e0y. \u0110i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 cho th\u1ea5y s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh, s\u1ef1 hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 c\u1ee7a ng\u00f4i sao sinh n\u0103m 1993. V\u00e0 vi\u1ec7c anh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ra s\u00e2n ngay t\u1eeb \u0111\u1ea7u \u1edf tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p Palestine c\u0169ng l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u kh\u00f4ng qu\u00e1 b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Tien ve Do Hung Dung\" title=\"Ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 \u0110\u1ed7 H\u00f9ng D\u0169ng\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/2/dt-olympic-viet-nam-co-hoi-nao-cho-nhom-tan-binh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>&nbsp;</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/dt-olympic-viet-nam-co-hoi-nao-cho-nhom-tan-binh-168-192576.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/2/dt-olympic-viet-nam-co-hoi-nao-cho-nhom-tan-binh.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/dt-olympic-viet-nam-co-hoi-nao-cho-nhom-tan-binh-168-192576.html\">\u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam: C\u01a1 h\u1ed9i n\u00e0o cho nh\u00f3m t\u00e2n binh?</span><br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div>\r\n9. Ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 c\u00e1nh Quang H\u1ea3i<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u1ea5n gi\u1eef h\u00e0nh lang c\u00e1nh tr\u00e1i c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 s\u1ebd l\u00e0 ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 c\u00f4ng Quang H\u1ea3i. L\u00e0 m\u1eabu ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 \u0111a n\u0103ng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u00e1 \u1edf hai c\u00e1nh c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u1edf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 trung t\u00e2m, Quang H\u1ea3i nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng s\u1ebd l\u00e0 l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn c\u1ee7a HLV Park Hang Seo cho tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1edbi.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">L\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00f9ng c\u1ee7a U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam t\u1ea1i VCK U23 ch\u00e2u \u00c1 2018 nh\u01b0ng khi tr\u1edf v\u1ec1 CLB H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i, Quang H\u1ea3i \u0111\u00e3 g\u1eb7p r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n trong giai \u0111o\u1ea1n \u0111\u1ea7u m\u00f9a khi nhi\u1ec1u tr\u1eadn ph\u1ea3i ng\u1ed3i d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb. Tuy nhi\u00ean Quang H\u1ea3i c\u00e0ng ch\u01a1i c\u00e0ng &lsquo;n\u00f3ng m\u00e1y&rsquo;. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">L\u00fac n\u00e0y anh \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 9 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng v\u00e0 ch\u1ec9 c\u00f2n k\u00e9m ch\u00e2n s\u00fat n\u1ed9i c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u b\u00e0n th\u1eafng nh\u1ea5t V-League 2018 l\u00e0 Nguy\u1ec5n Ti\u1ebfn Linh \u0111\u00fang hai b\u00e0n. Kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng ghi b\u00e0n \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a Quang H\u1ea3i s\u1ebd l\u00e0 c\u01a1 s\u1edf gi\u00fap anh c\u00f3 su\u1ea5t \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh t\u1ea1i Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam t\u1ea1i gi\u1ea3i giao h\u1eefu Vinaphone Cup.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<h2>10. H\u1ed9 c\u00f4ng Nguy\u1ec5n C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u1edf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed h\u1ed9 c\u00f4ng r\u1ea5t c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 s\u1ebd l\u00e0 ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng. V\u1edbi kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng r\u1ed9ng, thi \u0111\u1ea5u n\u0103ng n\u1ed5 v\u00e0 thu h\u00fat s\u1ef1 quan t\u00e2m c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng, C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng s\u1ebd t\u1ea1o ra nh\u1eefng kho\u1ea3ng tr\u1ed1ng cho \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i l\u1eadp c\u00f4ng.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">L\u00e0 m\u1eabu c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u00f3 k\u1ef9 thu\u1eadt, t\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ed9, C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 ghi r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u b\u00e0n th\u1eafng t\u1ea1i V-League m\u00f9a n\u00e0y. Do \u0111\u00f3 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng HLV Park Hang Seo trao c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i cho C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng l\u00e0 r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Cong Phuong chua co the luc tot nhat sau khi vua binh phuc chan thuong\" title=\"C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng ch\u01b0a c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u1ef1c t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t sau khi v\u1eeba b\u00ecnh ph\u1ee5c ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/29/cong-phuong-truot-bai-kiem-tra-the-luc-tai-dt-olympic-viet-nam.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>&nbsp;</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>11. Trung phong Nguy\u1ec5n Anh \u0110\u1ee9c<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">D\u00f9 \u0111\u00e3 \u1edf tu\u1ed5i 33 song Anh \u0110\u1ee9c v\u1eabn l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trung phong c\u00f3 vai tr\u00f2 \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t quan tr\u1ecdng tr\u00ean \u0110T Vi\u1ec7t Nam. Vi\u1ec7c anh xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n \u1edf \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam cho th\u1ea5y ni\u1ec1m tin c\u1ee7a HLV Park Hang Seo v\u1edbi Vua ph\u00e1 l\u01b0\u1edbi V-League 2017.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">D\u00f9 thi \u0111\u1ea5u kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 nhanh nh\u1eb9n song kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng ch\u1ecdn v\u1ecb tr\u00ed c\u1ef1c t\u1ed1t v\u00e0 d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 c\u1ee7a Anh \u0110\u1ee9c gi\u00fap anh v\u1eabn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c xem l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t &lsquo;s\u00e1t th\u1ee7 v\u00f2ng c\u1ea5m&rsquo; \u0111\u00e1ng s\u1ee3. Do \u0111\u00f3 Anh \u0110\u1ee9c c\u00f3 l\u1ebd v\u1eabn s\u1ebd l\u00e0 l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn s\u1ed1 1 c\u1ee7a th\u1ea7y Park trong th\u1eddi gian ch\u1edd \u0111\u1ee3i nh\u1eefng \u0110\u1ee9c Chinh, Ti\u1ebfn Linh tr\u01b0\u1edfng th\u00e0nh.&nbsp;<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/nhan-dinh-u23-viet-nam-vs-u23-palestine-19h30-ngay-038-cho-con-mua-ban-thang-168-192600.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/3/nhan-dinh-u23-viet-nam-vs-u23-palestine-19h30-ngay-038-cho-con-mua-ban-thang.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/nhan-dinh-u23-viet-nam-vs-u23-palestine-19h30-ngay-038-cho-con-mua-ban-thang-168-192600.html\">Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs U23 Palestine (19h30 ng\u00e0y 3/8): Ch\u1edd c\u01a1n m\u01b0a b\u00e0n th\u1eafng</span><br>\r\nV\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c c\u1ea3 hai \u0110T U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs U23 Palestine \u0111\u1ec1u tung ra \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh m\u1ea1nh nh\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ec3 th\u1eed nghi\u1ec7m l\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u1edf gi\u1ea3i n\u00e0y, ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00e2m m\u1ed9 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn m\u1ed9t...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"U23 Viet Nam\" title=\"U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/3/lineup.png\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>\u0110\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh ra s\u00e2n d\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn c\u1ee7a U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam tr\u01b0\u1edbc Palestine</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\nMinh Long (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1936","checkdouble":"192601"},{"date":"07:24 03/08","title":"Barca s\u1eafp tr\u00ecnh l\u00e0ng k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c gia World Cup trong 24 gi\u1edd t\u1edbi","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/25/barca-sap-trinh-lang-ky-luc-gia-world-cup-trong-24-gio-toi.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Wilfried Zaha mu\u1ed1n t\u1edbi Chelsea, ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1edd Bi\u1ec3n Ng\u00e0 \u0111\u00e3 t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i gia h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi Crystal Palace \u0111\u1ec3 quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m t\u1edbi Stamford Bridge.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chelsea nh\u1eafm Zaha n\u00e2ng c\u1ea5p h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nD\u01b0\u1edbi th\u1eddi HLV Sarri, Chelsea m\u1edbi ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 duy nh\u1ea5t Jorginho l\u00e0 b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng, c\u00f2n th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Robert Green ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u1ebfn theo d\u1ea1ng chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng t\u1ef1 do. HLV ng\u01b0\u1eddi Italia \u0111ang kh\u00f4ng h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng v\u1edbi t\u00ecnh h\u00ecnh nh\u00e2n s\u1ef1 hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i, \u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 th\u00eam nh\u1eefng b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng n\u1eefa.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"C\u1ef1c n\u00f3ng Wilfried Zaha mu\u1ed1n t\u1edbi Chelsea h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"C\u1ef1c n\u00f3ng Wilfried Zaha mu\u1ed1n t\u1edbi Chelsea h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/24/Cuc-nong-Wilfried-Zaha-muon-toi-Chelsea-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Wilfried Zaha c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i kho\u00e1c \u00e1o Chelsea n\u1ebfu Willian ho\u1eb7c Hazard ra \u0111i</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nChelsea \u0111ang l\u00e0m m\u1ecdi c\u00e1ch \u0111\u1ec3 khi\u1ebfn HLV Sarri c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng. \u0110\u1ed9i ng\u0169 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a The Blues \u0111ang ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng h\u1ebft c\u00f4ng su\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 th\u00eam nh\u1eefng b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng m\u1edbi. Theo Mirror, Chelsea quan t\u00e2m Zaha c\u1ee7a Crystal Palace.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTrong nh\u1eefng m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 26 tu\u1ed5i duy tr\u00ec phong \u0111\u1ed9 \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng. M\u00f9a v\u1eeba qua d\u00f9 d\u00ednh ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng \u1edf giai \u0111o\u1ea1n \u0111\u1ea7u m\u00f9a nh\u01b0ng c\u1ef1u sao M.U ghi t\u1edbi 9 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng \u1edf Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh gi\u00fap Palace tr\u1ee5 h\u1ea1ng th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nHi\u1ec7n Willian v\u00e0 Eden Hazard \u0111ang l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o t\u1ea7m ng\u1eafm c\u1ee7a nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng l\u1edbn, n\u1ebfu m\u1ed9t trong hai c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y r\u1eddi Stamford Bridge ngay l\u1eadp t\u1ee9c Chelsea s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 Zaha. \u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh London s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng chi 50 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng mua c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1992.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Zaha b\u1eadt \u0111\u00e8n xanh cho Chelsea</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Wilfried Zaha mu\u1ed1n t\u1edbi Chelsea, theo Mirror, ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1edd Bi\u1ec3n Ng\u00e0 \u0111\u00e3 t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i gia h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi Crystal Palace \u0111\u1ec3 quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m t\u1edbi Stamford&nbsp;Bridge.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"M\u1ee5c ti\u00eau 50 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng b\u1eadt \u0111\u00e8n xanh cho Chelsea h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" title=\"M\u1ee5c ti\u00eau 50 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng b\u1eadt \u0111\u00e8n xanh cho Chelsea h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/5/13/Muc-tieu-50-trieu-bang-bat-den-xanh-cho-Chelsea-hinh-anh-2.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Zaha mu\u1ed1n kho\u00e1c \u00e1o Chelsea</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nPh\u00eda Palace \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb gia h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng m\u1edbi, song c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1992 \u0111\u00e3 t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i. Zaha \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u00e1nh ti\u1ebfng mu\u1ed1n ra \u0111i. Ng\u00f4i sao 26 tu\u1ed5i mu\u1ed1n h\u01b0\u1edfng m\u1ed9t m\u1ee9c l\u01b0\u01a1ng cao h\u01a1n, anh c\u0169ng mu\u1ed1n c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn m\u1ed9t CLB c\u00f3 tham v\u1ecdng l\u1edbn \u0111\u1ec3 hy v\u1ecdng gi\u00e0nh nh\u1eefng danh hi\u1ec7u.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNgo\u00e0i Chelsea th\u00ec <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/co-doi-bong-chi-40-trieu-bang-mua-hang-thai-mu-172-182476.html\" target=\"_blank\">Tottenham c\u0169ng mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 Zaha</span>, song ph\u00eda Chelsea s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng chi \u0111\u1ee7 50 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng nh\u01b0 Palace y\u00eau c\u1ea7u, trong khi \u0111\u00f3 Spurs ch\u1ec9 ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi t\u1ed1i \u0111a 40 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nC\u1ef1u sao M.U \u0111ang r\u1ea5t h\u00e1o h\u1ee9c \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c kho\u00e1c \u00e1o Chelsea, n\u1ebfu The Blues th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng h\u1ecd c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111i\u1ec1u m\u00ecnh c\u1ea7n l\u00e0 r\u1ea5t cao. V\u1edbi kinh nghi\u1ec7m t\u1eebng thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u1edf Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 26 tu\u1ed5i s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng m\u1ea5y kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n \u0111\u1ec3 h\u00f2a nh\u1eadp v\u00e0o l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i c\u1ee7a Chelsea.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nL\u00ea H\u01b0\u1eddng (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1935","checkdouble":"192602"},{"date":"07:45 03/08","title":"M\u1ee5c ti\u00eau c\u1ee7a Chelsea \u0111\u1ed3ng \u00fd \u1edf l\u1ea1i Serie A","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/2/10/muc-tieu-cua-chelsea-dong-y-o-lai-serie-a.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Trong m\u1ed9t di\u1ec5n bi\u1ebfn m\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 ch\u1ea1y c\u00e1nh Alessandro Florenzi \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ed3ng \u00fd gia h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi AS Roma k\u1ebft th\u00fac nh\u1eefng tin \u0111\u1ed3n chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng li\u00ean quan t\u1edbi CLB Chelsea.</h2><h2>Florenzi gia h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi Roma</h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u00e1ch \u0111\u00e2y ch\u01b0a l\u00e2u, b\u00e1o gi\u1edbi Italia \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u0103ng t\u1ea3i th\u00f4ng tin CLB Chelsea mu\u1ed1n chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ch\u1ea1y c\u00e1nh Alessandro Florenzi c\u1ee7a AS Roma. Theo t\u1edd&nbsp;Corriere dello Sport, Alessandro Florenzi \u0111ang \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c HLV Sarri \u0111\u1ec3 m\u1eaft t\u1edbi nh\u01b0 m\u1ed9t ph\u01b0\u01a1ng \u00e1n&nbsp;t\u0103ng c\u01b0\u1eddng&nbsp;s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh n\u01a1i tuy\u1ebfn gi\u1eefa c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00f4.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"M.U va Barca muon co Alessandro Florenzi\" title=\"M.U v\u00e0 Barca mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 Alessandro Florenzi\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/2/10/muc-tieu-cua-chelsea-dong-y-o-lai-serie-a.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>Florenzi \u0111\u1ed3ng \u00fd gia h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi AS Roma</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong b\u1ed1i c\u1ea3nh Florenzi \u0111ang b\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1ec1 m\u1ee9c l\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u1edbi n\u1ebfu \u1edf l\u1ea1i Roma, \u0111\u00e2y s\u1ebd l\u00e0 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i t\u1ed1t \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh London g\u1eedi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Italia. Tuy nhi\u00ean cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng khi ng\u00f4i sao ch\u1ea1y c\u00e1nh 27 tu\u1ed5i n\u00e0y ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c \u1edf l\u1ea1i g\u1eafn b\u00f3 v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Serie A.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong m\u1ed9t di\u1ec5n bi\u1ebfn m\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t, \u0111\u1ed9i ph\u00f3 Roma \u0111\u00e3 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh k\u00e9o d\u00e0i th\u1eddi gian ph\u1ee5c v\u1ee5 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Olimpico b\u1eb1ng c\u00e1ch \u0111\u1eb7t b\u00fat k\u00fd v\u00e0o m\u1ed9t h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng m\u1edbi c\u00f3 th\u1eddi h\u1ea1n 5 n\u0103m v\u00e0 s\u1ebd \u0111\u00e1o h\u1ea1n v\u00e0o n\u0103m 2023. \u0110i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y c\u0169ng kh\u00e9p l\u1ea1i nh\u1eefng th\u00f4ng tin chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng li\u00ean quan t\u1edbi Florenzi. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3, kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 Chelsea m\u00e0 c\u1ea3 Inter Milan v\u00e0 Atletico Madrid \u0111\u1ec1u r\u1ea5t mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ch\u1ea1y c\u00e1nh c\u1ee7a Roma.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Florenzi \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 224 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u00e1 cho AS Roma v\u00e0 28 l\u1ea7n kho\u00e1c \u00e1o \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Italia. Anh ch\u01a1i thu\u1ea7n \u1edf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 trung t\u00e2m v\u00e0 c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e1 t\u1ed1t \u1edf bi\u00ean ph\u1ea3i. Gi\u00e1 tr\u1ecb c\u1ee7a ng\u00f4i sao n\u00e0y \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1ecbnh gi\u00e1 v\u00e0o kho\u1ea3ng 30 tri\u1ec7u euro.</p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/nong-them-mot-cau-thu-chia-tay-mu-172-192598.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/1/nong-them-mot-cau-thu-chia-tay-mu.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/nong-them-mot-cau-thu-chia-tay-mu-172-192598.html\">N\u00f3ng: Th\u00eam m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 chia tay M.U</span><br>\r\nTrong m\u1ed9t di\u1ec5n bi\u1ebfn m\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t, th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh tr\u1ebb tu\u1ed5i Joel Pereira \u0111\u00e3 n\u00f3i l\u1eddi chia tay M.U \u0111\u1ec3 gia nh\u1eadp \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Vitoria Setubal theo d\u1ea1ng cho m\u01b0\u1ee3n.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/tin-chuyen-nhuong/barca-sap-trinh-lang-ky-luc-gia-world-cup-trong-24-gio-toi-187-192602.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/25/barca-sap-trinh-lang-ky-luc-gia-world-cup-trong-24-gio-toi.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/tin-chuyen-nhuong/barca-sap-trinh-lang-ky-luc-gia-world-cup-trong-24-gio-toi-187-192602.html\">Barca s\u1eafp tr\u00ecnh l\u00e0ng k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c gia World Cup trong 24 gi\u1edd t\u1edbi</span><br>\r\nTheo t\u1edd Diario Sport, CLB Barcelona \u0111\u00e3 ho\u00e0n t\u1ea5t v\u1ee5 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 c\u00e1nh ng\u01b0\u1eddi Senegal, Moussa Wagu\u00e9, ng\u01b0\u1eddi v\u1eeba l\u1eadp k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c ghi b\u00e0n t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Minh Long (TTVN)<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1934","checkdouble":"192603"},{"date":"08:05 03/08","title":"4 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u1ea1i chi\u1ebfn v\u00ec sao MU","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2016/12/18/4-doi-bong-hoi-mua-marcos-rojo.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 Everton mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u01b0a Marcos Rojo r\u1eddi MU, theo The Sun, ngo\u00e0i \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh ph\u1ed1 C\u1ea3ng th\u00ec 3 CLB kh\u00e1c c\u0169ng mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Argentina.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">4 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng quan t\u00e2m Marcos Rojo</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTrong th\u1eddi gian g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y, trung v\u1ec7 Marcos Rojo c\u1ee7a M.U b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o t\u1ea7m ng\u1eafm c\u1ee7a nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng l\u1edbn. <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/everton-chi-chap-nhan-chi-30-trieu-bang-mua-marcos-rojo-neu-172-192428.html\" target=\"_blank\">Everton mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 Rojo</span>, h\u1ecd ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi 30 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng cho th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y.&nbsp;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"4 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u01b0a h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 Marcos Rojo r\u1eddi MU h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"4 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u01b0a h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 Marcos Rojo r\u1eddi MU h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/2/18/4-doi-bong-muon-dua-hau-ve-Marcos-Rojo-roi-MU-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>4 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng h\u1ecfi mua Marcos Rojo</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nTuy nhi\u00ean, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh ph\u1ed1 C\u1ea3ng s\u1ebd ch\u1ec9 k\u00fd h\u01a1pk \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 28 tu\u1ed5i n\u1ebfu anh gi\u1ea3m l\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u1eeb 120.000 b\u1ea3ng/tu\u1ea7n xu\u1ed1ng 60.000 b\u1ea3ng/tu\u1ea7n.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nHi\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Goodison Park v\u1eabn \u0111ang \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1990. Theo The Sun, kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh ph\u1ed1 C\u1ea3ng m\u00e0 3 CLB <br>\r\nkh\u00e1c \u0111\u00e3 nh\u1ea3y v\u00e0o cu\u1ed9c \u0111ua gi\u00e0nh ch\u1eef k\u00fd c\u1ee7a ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Argentina.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nC\u1ee5 th\u1ec3, PSG, Marseille v\u00e0 Zenit St Petersburg c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u00e1nh ti\u1ebfng mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf. Nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0y c\u0169ng ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi ra m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ee7 l\u1edbn \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1ea1nh tranh ch\u1eef k\u00fd c\u1ee7a Marcos Rojo v\u1edbi Everton.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>M.U s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ec3 Marcos Rojo ra \u0111i</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nhi\u1ec1u CLB mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u01b0a Marcos Rojo r\u1eddi MU, kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng h\u1ecd c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111i\u1ec1u m\u00ecnh c\u1ea7n l\u00e0 ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3. \u0110\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Old Trafford s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng b\u00e1n c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1990 \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ea5y ng\u00e2n s\u00e1ch chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 m\u1ed9t trung v\u1ec7 kh\u1ee7ng trong th\u1eddi gian c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a k\u1ef3 CN H\u00e8 2018.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"4 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u1ea1i chi\u1ebfn v\u00ec sao MU h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" title=\"4 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u1ea1i chi\u1ebfn v\u00ec sao MU h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2017/11/16/4-doi-bong-dai-chien-vi-sao-MU-hinh-anh-2.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>M.U s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng b\u00e1n Marcos Rojo&nbsp;</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nTheo Daily Mail, M.U \u0111\u00e3 ch\u1ed1t Mina c\u1ee7a Barca l\u00e0 m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng \u1edf H\u00e8 n\u00e0y. \u0110\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Old Trafford ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi 35 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng mua c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Colombia, \u0111\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho l\u00e0 s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 khi\u1ebfn Barca h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTrong nh\u1eefng n\u0103m g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y, Marcos Rojo thi \u0111\u1ea5u kh\u00f4ng qu\u00e1 \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng. M\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba r\u1ed3i anh th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean d\u00ednh ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng, v\u1edbi m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3ng g\u00f3p cho \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng, vi\u1ec7c anh ra \u0111i c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng qu\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ebfn ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh c\u1ee7a M.U.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nMourinho \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho l\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng v\u1edbi k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch mua s\u1eafm c\u1ee7a M.U \u1edf H\u00e8 2018, \u00f4ng th\u1ea7y ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ed3 mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 4 \u0111\u1ebfn 5 t\u00e2n binh kh\u1ee7ng. Tuy nhi\u00ean, \u0111\u1ebfn th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 Fred v\u00e0 Dalot l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u01b0\u01a1ng Ng\u00e2n (TTVN)</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1933","checkdouble":"192604"},{"date":"08:19 03/08","title":"M\u1ee5c ti\u00eau 50 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng \"b\u1eadt \u0111\u00e8n xanh\" cho Chelsea","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/5/7/zaha-moi-goi-chelsea.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Wilfried Zaha mu\u1ed1n t\u1edbi Chelsea, ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1edd Bi\u1ec3n Ng\u00e0 \u0111\u00e3 t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i gia h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi Crystal Palace \u0111\u1ec3 quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m t\u1edbi Stamford Bridge.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chelsea nh\u1eafm Zaha n\u00e2ng c\u1ea5p h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nD\u01b0\u1edbi th\u1eddi HLV Sarri, Chelsea m\u1edbi ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 duy nh\u1ea5t Jorginho l\u00e0 b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng, c\u00f2n th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Robert Green ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u1ebfn theo d\u1ea1ng chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng t\u1ef1 do. HLV ng\u01b0\u1eddi Italia \u0111ang kh\u00f4ng h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng v\u1edbi t\u00ecnh h\u00ecnh nh\u00e2n s\u1ef1 hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i, \u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 th\u00eam nh\u1eefng b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng n\u1eefa.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"C\u1ef1c n\u00f3ng Wilfried Zaha mu\u1ed1n t\u1edbi Chelsea h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"C\u1ef1c n\u00f3ng Wilfried Zaha mu\u1ed1n t\u1edbi Chelsea h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/24/Cuc-nong-Wilfried-Zaha-muon-toi-Chelsea-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Wilfried Zaha c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i kho\u00e1c \u00e1o Chelsea n\u1ebfu Willian ho\u1eb7c Hazard ra \u0111i</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nChelsea \u0111ang l\u00e0m m\u1ecdi c\u00e1ch \u0111\u1ec3 khi\u1ebfn HLV Sarri c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng. \u0110\u1ed9i ng\u0169 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a The Blues \u0111ang ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng h\u1ebft c\u00f4ng su\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 th\u00eam nh\u1eefng b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng m\u1edbi. Theo Mirror, Chelsea quan t\u00e2m Zaha c\u1ee7a Crystal Palace.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTrong nh\u1eefng m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 26 tu\u1ed5i duy tr\u00ec phong \u0111\u1ed9 \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng. M\u00f9a v\u1eeba qua d\u00f9 d\u00ednh ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng \u1edf giai \u0111o\u1ea1n \u0111\u1ea7u m\u00f9a nh\u01b0ng c\u1ef1u sao M.U ghi t\u1edbi 9 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng \u1edf Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh gi\u00fap Palace tr\u1ee5 h\u1ea1ng th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nHi\u1ec7n Willian v\u00e0 Eden Hazard \u0111ang l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o t\u1ea7m ng\u1eafm c\u1ee7a nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng l\u1edbn, n\u1ebfu m\u1ed9t trong hai c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y r\u1eddi Stamford Bridge ngay l\u1eadp t\u1ee9c Chelsea s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 Zaha. \u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh London s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng chi 50 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng mua c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1992.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Zaha b\u1eadt \u0111\u00e8n xanh cho Chelsea</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Wilfried Zaha mu\u1ed1n t\u1edbi Chelsea, theo Mirror, ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1edd Bi\u1ec3n Ng\u00e0 \u0111\u00e3 t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i gia h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi Crystal Palace \u0111\u1ec3 quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m t\u1edbi Stamford&nbsp;Bridge.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"M\u1ee5c ti\u00eau 50 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng b\u1eadt \u0111\u00e8n xanh cho Chelsea h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" title=\"M\u1ee5c ti\u00eau 50 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng b\u1eadt \u0111\u00e8n xanh cho Chelsea h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/5/13/Muc-tieu-50-trieu-bang-bat-den-xanh-cho-Chelsea-hinh-anh-2.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Zaha mu\u1ed1n kho\u00e1c \u00e1o Chelsea</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nPh\u00eda Palace \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb gia h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng m\u1edbi, song c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1992 \u0111\u00e3 t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i. Zaha \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u00e1nh ti\u1ebfng mu\u1ed1n ra \u0111i. Ng\u00f4i sao 26 tu\u1ed5i mu\u1ed1n h\u01b0\u1edfng m\u1ed9t m\u1ee9c l\u01b0\u01a1ng cao h\u01a1n, anh c\u0169ng mu\u1ed1n c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn m\u1ed9t CLB c\u00f3 tham v\u1ecdng l\u1edbn \u0111\u1ec3 hy v\u1ecdng gi\u00e0nh nh\u1eefng danh hi\u1ec7u.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNgo\u00e0i Chelsea th\u00ec <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/co-doi-bong-chi-40-trieu-bang-mua-hang-thai-mu-172-182476.html\" target=\"_blank\">Tottenham c\u0169ng mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 Zaha</span>, song ph\u00eda Chelsea s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng chi \u0111\u1ee7 50 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng nh\u01b0 Palace y\u00eau c\u1ea7u, trong khi \u0111\u00f3 Spurs ch\u1ec9 ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi t\u1ed1i \u0111a 40 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nC\u1ef1u sao M.U \u0111ang r\u1ea5t h\u00e1o h\u1ee9c \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c kho\u00e1c \u00e1o Chelsea, n\u1ebfu The Blues th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng h\u1ecd c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111i\u1ec1u m\u00ecnh c\u1ea7n l\u00e0 r\u1ea5t cao. V\u1edbi kinh nghi\u1ec7m t\u1eebng thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u1edf Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 26 tu\u1ed5i s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng m\u1ea5y kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n \u0111\u1ec3 h\u00f2a nh\u1eadp v\u00e0o l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i c\u1ee7a Chelsea.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nL\u00ea H\u01b0\u1eddng (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1932","checkdouble":"192605"}]}